      <title>欢迎！</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/04/welcome/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/04/welcome/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>你好呀，欢迎来到洛奇亚的博客。<br>侧边栏中可以切换到不同的页面，去逛一逛吧。（手机端点左上角）</p></blockquote><h1 id="合集"><a href="#合集" class="headerlink" title="合集"></a>合集</h1><h2 id="方块竞速"><a href="#方块竞速" class="headerlink" title="方块竞速"></a>方块竞速</h2><p>我的第一个项目。看介绍点击<a href="https://lqsnow.top/2022/12/12/BlockRacing%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/">游戏介绍</a>，下载插件去<a href="https://github.com/LQSnow/BlockRacing/releases/">BlockRacing Releases</a></p><p><a href="https://lqsnow.top/2022/12/12/BlockRacing%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/">游戏介绍</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/LQSnow/BlockRacing">Github</a></p><h2 id="Minecraft新手教学"><a href="#Minecraft新手教学" class="headerlink" title="Minecraft新手教学"></a>Minecraft新手教学</h2><p>如果想先免费体验一下MC，可以直接看<a href="https://lqsnow.top/2022/12/06/Minecraft%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/">Minecraft下载与安装</a>，用离线账号登录（免费），等决定好了再买也不迟。</p><p><a href="https://lqsnow.top/2022/12/05/Minecraft%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/">Minecraft购买教程</a><br><a href="https://lqsnow.top/2022/12/06/Minecraft%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/">Minecraft下载与安装</a> </p>]]></content>
      
      
      
